{"kind":"article","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/gettingstarted"]}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Essentials","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Tokens","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Themes","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Components","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Modules"],"anchor":"Essentials","generated":true}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Integrate OUDS","anchor":"Integrate-OUDS","type":"heading"},{"level":3,"text":"Use Swift Package Manager","anchor":"Use-Swift-Package-Manager","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to add the iOS library of "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Unified Design System"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":", you need to add our "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" into your project."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To do that, add a new "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"package dependency"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" to your "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" project by refering to it by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You are free to choose whether or not you want a branch or a specific tag, pick the solution you want."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki\/50-%E2%80%90-About-versions,-releases-and-builds"},{"type":"text","text":" for more details about versions, releases and tags. You can find release tags (e.g. "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"1.0.0","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":") and release candidates tags (e.g. "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"1.0.0-rc3","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"text":"Import the librairies you need","anchor":"Import-the-librairies-you-need","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You should use one (or several) of the following imports for your needs, which are basically "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift Package","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" products."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"We recommend to embed in your apps only the ones you need to avoid to embed useless assets.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Tip","style":"tip","type":"aside"},{"code":["import OUDSThemesContract \/\/ If you want to define your theme, use themes or OUDSThemeableView","import OUDSModules \/\/ To use modules","import OUDSComponents \/\/ To use components","import OUDSThemesOrange \/\/ To use the default Orange theme","import OUDSThemesOrangeCompact \/\/ To use the Orange Compact theme","import OUDSThemesSosh \/\/ To use the Sosh theme","import OUDSThemesWireframe \/\/ To use the Wireframe theme","import OUDSTokensComponent \/\/ If you need to override or use directly components tokens","import OUDSTokenSemantic \/\/ If you need to override or use directly semantic tokens","import OUDSTokensRaw \/\/ If you need to override or use directly raw tokens","import OUDSFoundations \/\/ For some utilities"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"level":3,"text":"Or more simple, import umbrella library","anchor":"Or-more-simple-import-umbrella-library","type":"heading"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"We do not recommend this solution because from our point of view use of tailored imports is better to import only the needed elements.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"use of umbrella products can increase app sizes and needed storage because it emebds plenty of assets (images, fonts, etc.)","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and useless constants.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Note","style":"note","type":"aside"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Import the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift Package","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" product which suits your needs:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"header":"row","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Umbrella","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Description","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUI","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above and all themes","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrange","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Orange Compact themes","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUIWireframe","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Wireframe theme","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrangeSosh","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Sosh themes","type":"text"}]}]]],"type":"table"},{"level":3,"text":"Chose your theme","anchor":"Chose-your-theme","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Unified Design System","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" framework provides today four themes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"header":"row","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Theme","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Description","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The default one for Orange products and can be enriched \/ derivated","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Compact","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For some Orange products with heavy \/ rich UI and dimensions constraints","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sosh","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For Sosh products","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Wireframe","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For mockups, prototypes and prooves of concepts witouth Orange-flavoured styles","type":"text"}]}]]],"type":"table"},{"level":3,"text":"Apply a theme","anchor":"Apply-a-theme","type":"heading"},{"numberOfColumns":2,"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You will need to use for your application root view the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/oudsthemeableview\/"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/themes"},{"type":"text","text":" also."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This special view is here to define some elements as environment variables and injects the choosen theme."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"code":["@main","struct YourApp: App {","    var body: some Scene {","       WindowGroup {","          OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","          }","       }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"type":"row"},{"numberOfColumns":2,"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then get the current applied theme in your views and use the tokens you want."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The tokens are wrapped in providers with clear names, you only need to choose the ones you want."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"code":["\/\/ Use it in views as an environment variable","@Environment(\\.theme) var theme"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"type":"row"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Keep in mind only one theme can be used within one ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Tip","style":"tip","type":"aside"},{"level":3,"text":"Trick for Xcode Preview","anchor":"Trick-for-Xcode-Preview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you use Xcode "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"#Preview"},{"type":"text","text":" blocks, you will have to be sure the theme is instanciated and injected through the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because it is not possible today to override the legit "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"#Preview"},{"type":"text","text":" block, you can instead use some of our utilities to wrap your content"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"inside the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"type":"text","text":" automatically. These utilities come with the themes modules. Without them you may face errors about undefined theme."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ Apply Orange theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .orangePreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Orange Compact theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .orangeCompactPreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Sosh theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .soshPreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Wireframe theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .wireframePreview()","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"text":"How to add the package as dependency, import libraries and use theme and components for your apps.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/GettingStarted","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","modules":[{"name":"Welcome to Orange Unified Design System"}],"role":"article","title":"Getting Started with OUDS","images":[{"identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png","type":"card"}]},"references":{"https://ios.unified-design-system.orange.com/documentation/ouds/oudsthemeableview/":{"title":"OUDSThemeableView","url":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/oudsthemeableview\/","identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/oudsthemeableview\/","type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"}]},"ic_unified_ds.png":{"identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png","alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesContract\/ic_unified_ds.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image"},"ic_component_intro.png":{"identifier":"ic_component_intro.png","alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesContract\/ic_component_intro.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/Modules":{"images":[{"identifier":"ic_module_intro.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"ic_module_intro.png","type":"card"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Modules","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/modules","role":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"module"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" can be seen as a set of features and components to fill a need.","type":"text"}],"kind":"article","title":"Modules","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract":{"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract","abstract":[{"text":"Orange Unified Design System: Build Sharper. Ship faster. Perform better.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"Welcome to Orange Unified Design System","type":"topic"},"ic_module_intro.png":{"identifier":"ic_module_intro.png","alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesContract\/ic_module_intro.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/Themes":{"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/themes","abstract":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Themes","type":"text"}]},{"text":" are applications of specific values for ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"components tokens","type":"text"}]},{"text":" and dimensionsemantic tokens_ using in the end ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"raw tokens","type":"text"}]},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"theme","type":"text"}]},{"text":" contains any relevant tokens which can be used for components rendering.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"theme","type":"text"}]},{"text":" can use its own assets like fonts and icons.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Themes","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_intro.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"ic_theme_intro.png","type":"card"}],"title":"Themes"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/Components":{"